{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2070, "height": 2786, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指东汉时期的杜诗事典，下联典指唐朝时期的杜如晦事典。", "block_bbox": [276, 240, 1510, 293], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "8.学业醇儒富；星斗焕文章。", "block_bbox": [274, 309, 816, 359], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为佚名集唐诗联。上联见杜甫《赠特进汝阳王二十韵》，下联见杜牧《华清宫三十韵》。\n", "block_bbox": [183, 376, 1699, 493], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "8.草堂留后世；诗圣著千秋。", "block_bbox": [271, 512, 812, 560], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为朱德（1886~1976）撰书四川省成都杜甫草堂联。", "block_bbox": [271, 579, 1312, 630], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "9.守道还如周柱史；著书曾学郑司农。", "block_bbox": [270, 649, 981, 698], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为集唐诗联。上联见杜牧《送国棋王逢》，下联见刘禹锡《送裴处士应制举诗》。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 717, 1694, 834], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "10.云霞晴光转物候；春夜喜雨知时节。", "block_bbox": [312, 853, 1037, 903], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为集唐诗联。上联化出于杜审言《和晋陵陆丞早春游望》：“独有宦游人，偏惊物候新。云霞出海曙，梅柳渡江春。淑气催黄鸟，晴光转绿苹。忽闻歌古调，归思欲沾襟”。下联化出于杜甫《春夜喜雨》：“好雨知时节，当春乃发生。随风潜入夜，润物细无声。野径云俱黑，江船火独明。晓看红湿处，花重锦官城。\n", "block_bbox": [183, 919, 1695, 1238], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "11.枫林绿树丹青合；玉杯锦席风云流。", "block_bbox": [278, 1256, 1003, 1307], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为唐朝诗人杜甫诗句联。上联见《夔州歌十绝句》一句“枫林橘树丹青合”\n", "block_bbox": [186, 1321, 1693, 1437], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "12.梦醒扬州甘薄幸；心忧社稷老风尘。", "block_bbox": [280, 1455, 1004, 1507], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联化于唐诗句。上联见杜牧《七绝遣怀》“落魄江湖载酒行，楚腰纤细掌中轻。十年一觉扬州梦，赢得青楼薄幸名”。下联见杜审言诗。", "block_bbox": [184, 1524, 1693, 1641], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "13.锦水春风公占却；草堂人日我归来。", "block_bbox": [280, 1659, 1005, 1710], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为清代书法家何绍基撰杜工部（杜甫）祠联。", "block_bbox": [277, 1725, 1207, 1780], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "14.世上创痍笔底波澜，民间疾苦诗中圣哲。", "block_bbox": [278, 1795, 1060, 1846], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联为郭沫若撰书四川省成都杜甫草堂联。", "block_bbox": [278, 1861, 1080, 1914], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "15.十二代燕翼贻谋，名留奕世思荀鹤；亿万年蝉联衍庆，叙接花溪祀玉龙。此为四川省旺苍县木门镇杜氏宗祠有副石刻对联，清光绪廪生杜维翰撰。", "block_bbox": [276, 1930, 1677, 2048], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "16.南阳得政歌炎汉，西蜀诗才显盛唐。", "block_bbox": [279, 2065, 1007, 2117], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜氏浣花堂联。", "block_bbox": [277, 2133, 570, 2183], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "17.意随流水俱远；心与白鹤同闲。", "block_bbox": [277, 2202, 921, 2251], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "清末南北大侠、自然门创始人、武术家杜心武撰联。", "block_bbox": [276, 2267, 1244, 2320], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "18.祁公开两省东南闽粤总一家，世泽承中宪克绍箕裘二百年。", "block_bbox": [275, 2336, 1421, 2387], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "横额：翰林风月", "block_bbox": [275, 2403, 586, 2453], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "福建省厦门杏林马銮杜氏家庙联。", "block_bbox": [274, 2470, 906, 2521], "block_id": 24, "block_order": 25}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "三四二", "block_bbox": [1821, 2099, 1872, 2216], "block_id": 25, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.815396785736084, "coordinate": [183.11895751953125, 919.5447998046875, 1695.68408203125, 1238.2037353515625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7204543948173523, "coordinate": [184.2115478515625, 1524.062744140625, 1693.404541015625, 1641.703369140625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7074503898620605, "coordinate": [186.6085205078125, 1321.734130859375, 1693.6033935546875, 1437.493896484375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7073781490325928, "coordinate": [183.74444580078125, 376.14703369140625, 1699.11083984375, 493.8941650390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7062530517578125, "coordinate": [184.48748779296875, 717.056640625, 1694.06103515625, 834.900634765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6250323057174683, "coordinate": [276.77435302734375, 240.08770751953125, 1510.597412109375, 293.3826904296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.622963547706604, "coordinate": [276.2108154296875, 1930.88671875, 1677.9185791015625, 2048.65283203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.612869381904602, "coordinate": [276.061767578125, 2267.9384765625, 1244.77587890625, 2320.0234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6018496155738831, "coordinate": [275.04974365234375, 2336.00732421875, 1421.779541015625, 2387.50634765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5995672345161438, "coordinate": [271.88836669921875, 579.6749877929688, 1312.2607421875, 630.8436889648438]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5916947722434998, "coordinate": [280.7347412109375, 1455.926025390625, 1004.036376953125, 1507.633544921875