杜甫《春夜喜雨》：“好雨知时节，当春乃发生。随风潜入夜，润物细无声。野径云俱黑，江船火独明。晓看红湿处，花重锦官城。\n\n\n\n11.枫林绿树丹青合；玉杯锦席风云流。\n\n此联为唐朝诗人杜甫诗句联。上联见《夔州歌十绝句》一句“枫林橘树丹青合”\n\n\n\n12.梦醒扬州甘薄幸；心忧社稷老风尘。\n\n此联化于唐诗句。上联见杜牧《七绝遣怀》“落魄江湖载酒行，楚腰纤细掌中轻。十年一觉扬州梦，赢得青楼薄幸名”。下联见杜审言诗。\n\n13.锦水春风公占却；草堂人日我归来。\n\n此联为清代书法家何绍基撰杜工部（杜甫）祠联。\n\n14.世上创痍笔底波澜，民间疾苦诗中圣哲。\n\n此联为郭沫若撰书四川省成都杜甫草堂联。\n\n15.十二代燕翼贻谋，名留奕世思荀鹤；亿万年蝉联衍庆，叙接花溪祀玉龙。此为四川省旺苍县木门镇杜氏宗祠有副石刻对联，清光绪廪生杜维翰撰。\n\n16.南阳得政歌炎汉，西蜀诗才显盛唐。\n\n杜氏浣花堂联。\n\n17.意随流水俱远；心与白鹤同闲。\n\n清末南北大侠、自然门创始人、武术家杜心武撰联。\n\n18.祁公开两省东南闽粤总一家，世泽承中宪克绍箕裘二百年。\n\n横额：翰林风月\n\n福建省厦门杏林马銮杜氏家庙联。", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//1325e3b4-a561-4a67-afa4-4156d43c2288/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A29%3A01Z%2F-1%2F%2F4d51b27a32aea0613436dcc5abcc9ac1f81553b45081db4d055406c18e041314", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//1325e3b4-a561-4a67-afa4-4156d43c2288/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A29%3A02Z%2F-1%2F%2F50653cfb9f9e97fab246aeacb284a48a0fcdc670941c5035b6c73c95fb4f0af4", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//1325e3b4-a561-4a67-afa4-4156d43c2288/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A29%3A02Z%2F-1%2F%2F7074cfd673fb836ec3677bdeeeb77864f672f80b63222a8ecee665d2b689b50c", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//1325e3b4-a561-4a67-afa4-4156d43c2288/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A29%3A02Z%2F-1%2F%2F8847652088ecb2b4bf213a9d0e5424f6ffa52f7eaddc5ed9346a087bdde71659"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//1325e3b4-a561-4a6